title: UFC 78 Validation
description:
UFC 78: Validation was a mixed martial arts event held by the Ultimate Fighting Championship (UFC), that took place on November 17, 2007 at the Prudential Center in Newark, New Jersey.[1] Validation was the first UFC event held in New Jersey since June 4, 2005&#039;s UFC 53: Heavy Hitters in Atlantic City.
